    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12">
    <p class="inline-block ">
      <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt "></i>We are located at our streaming service.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12">
    <p class="inline-block ">
      <i class="fas fa-at "></i>info@mockbuster.co.uk</br>
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12">
    <p class="inline-block ">
      <i class="fas fa-phone "></i>0208 12345678
